*Tapes are sold separately.

ResourceSink_Catwalks_C.name: Modern Catwalks
ResourceSink_Catwalks_C.description: Ever wanted to admire your factories from a safe and convenient place? Build some Walkways and get inspired by your own labour to do even better!

ResourceSink_Customizer_Asphalt_Foundati.name: Asphalt Foundation Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_Asphalt_Foundati.description: Adds the Asphalt Foundation Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Foundation or Ramp.

ResourceSink_Customizer_Concrete_Foundat.name: Concrete Foundation Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_Concrete_Foundat.description: Adds the Concrete Foundation Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Foundation or Ramp.

ResourceSink_FoundationExpansionPack_C.name: Double Ramp Set
ResourceSink_FoundationExpansionPack_C.description: Never again will you build a Ramp one step at a time. Take over the world efficiently, increase your productivity and enjoy building in diagonal with the new Double Ramps!

ResourceSink_Customizer_GripMetal_Founda.name: Grip Metal Foundation Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_GripMetal_Founda.description: Adds the Grip Metal Foundation Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Foundation or Ramp.

ResourceSink_Customizer_PolishedConcrete.name: Coated Concrete Foundation Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_PolishedConcrete.description: Adds the Coated Concrete Foundation Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Foundation or Ramp.

ResourceSink_Walkways_C.name: Industrial Walkways
ResourceSink_Walkways_C.description: Ever wanted to admire your factories from a safe and convenient place? Build some Walkways and get inspired by your own labour to do even better!

ResourceSink_HalfFoundations_C.name: Half Foundation Set
ResourceSink_HalfFoundations_C.description:
Are the regular Foundations too big for your needs? Want to keep some space in your floor for Conveyor Lifts?
Introducing: Half Foundations! Only half the size, for the full price!

ResourceSink_QuarterPipeExtensions_C.name: Quarter Pipe Extensions Pack
ResourceSink_QuarterPipeExtensions_C.description: Bring your Quarter Pipes to new heights, or simply add rounded accents to your factory design, with the brand new special Quarter Pipe Extensions.

ResourceSink_CeilingLight_C.name: Indoor Lighting
ResourceSink_CeilingLight_C.description: Ceiling Lights are the perfect choice for indoor illumination. Simply attach them to the ceiling, hook up power, and watch your conveyor belts shine bright even in the darkest of factories.

ResourceSink_LightTower_C.name: Flood Lights
ResourceSink_LightTower_C.description: Specifically designed to illuminate outdoor areas, the Flood Lights are the perfect choice for lighting up construction sites or outposts. Their height makes them tower over even the largest of buildings. And for additional convenience the Wall version can be placed on any wall, for indoor settings or if more precise light placement is required.

ResourceSink_StreetLight_C.name: Street Light
ResourceSink_StreetLight_C.description: No more night-time related walkway accidents involving Trucks and poor lighting conditions! Light up those pathways and roads using the FICSIT Street Lights!

ResourceSink_Customizer_ConcreteWallMate.name: Concrete Wall Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_ConcreteWallMate.description: Adds the Concrete Wall Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Wall.

ResourceSink_Customizer_SteelWallMateria.name: Steel Wall Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_SteelWallMateria.description: Adds the Steel Wall Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Wall.

ResourceSink_HyperTubeWallAttachements_C.name: Hypertube Wall Attachments
ResourceSink_HyperTubeWallAttachements_C.description: Never again will a wall stop you from swooping through your factory. With the new next-gen Hypertube Wall Hole included in this pack, speed has no limits!

ResourceSink_WallPowerPoles_C.name: Wall Power Outlets Mk.1
ResourceSink_WallPowerPoles_C.description: Tired of bulky power poles? Save space and organize an efficient power grid in your factory with the all new and revolutionary Power Outlets for walls and ceilings!

ResourceSink_WallPowerPolesMK2_C.name: Wall Power Outlets Mk.2
ResourceSink_WallPowerPolesMK2_C.description: Tired of bulky power poles? Save space and organize an efficient power grid in your factory with the all new and revolutionary Power Outlets for walls and ceilings!

ResourceSink_WallPowerPolesMK3_C.name: Wall Power Outlets Mk.3
ResourceSink_WallPowerPolesMK3_C.description: Tired of bulky power poles? Save space and organize an efficient power grid in your factory with the all new and revolutionary Power Outlets for walls and ceilings!

ResourceSink_DoorWalls_Normal_C.name: Door Walls
ResourceSink_DoorWalls_Normal_C.description: Space dilation is still in the R&D phase at FICSIT research facilities. It's not yet recommended to try walking through walls. Purchase a Door today for safe factory traversal!

ResourceSink_GoldenCart_C.name: Golden FICSIT Factory Cart™
ResourceSink_GoldenCart_C.description: How did you even figure out how to get this? Whatever... You deserve it.

ResourceSink_GoldenCup_C.name: 'Employee of the Planet' Cup
ResourceSink_GoldenCup_C.description: This limited edition cup is only awarded to those Pioneers who have completed the last available stage of Project Assembly in its 'early design stage'.

ResourceSink_NoIndicator_PipelineMK1_C.name: Clean Pipeline Mk.1
ResourceSink_NoIndicator_PipelineMK1_C.description: This clean version of the Mk.1 Pipeline does not feature the external fluid indicator, sacrificing feedback for style.

ResourceSink_NoIndicator_PipelineMK2_C.name: Clean Pipeline Mk.2
ResourceSink_NoIndicator_PipelineMK2_C.description: This clean version of the Mk.2 Pipeline does not feature the external fluid indicator, sacrificing feedback for style.

ResourceSink_Roofs_Basic_C.name: FICSIT Roofs
ResourceSink_Roofs_Basic_C.description:
Every Pioneer deserves a Roof over their head and factory. Get this basic human need now for only 6 Coupons!

Once unlocked, Roof Materials will become available for purchase in the Customizer section of the AWESOME Shop. Do not miss out on those special looks!

ResourceSink_Customizer_GlassRoofMateria.name: Glass Roof Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_GlassRoofMateria.description: Adds the Glass Roof Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Roof.

ResourceSink_Roofs_Corners_C.name: FICSIT Roof Corners
ResourceSink_Roofs_Corners_C.description: New research has shown that repetitive Roof aesthetics reduce Pioneer efficiency. Solve your productivity issues today, with these versatile Roof Corner pieces!

ResourceSink_Customizer_SteelRoofMateria.name: Steel Roof Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_SteelRoofMateria.description: Adds the Steel Roof Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Roof.

ResourceSink_Customizer_TarRoofMaterial_.name: Tar Roof Material
ResourceSink_Customizer_TarRoofMaterial_.description: Adds the Tar Roof Material to the Customizer, from where it can be applied to any Roof.

ResourceSink_StatueSilverPioneer_C.name: Pretty Good Pioneering
ResourceSink_StatueSilverPioneer_C.description: Are you up for the challenge? Show your worth with this recognition efforts and proudly showcase it in your factory if you're really sure you deserve it.

ResourceSink_StatueLizardDoggo_C.name: Lizard Doggo
ResourceSink_StatueLizardDoggo_C.description: You love Doggos but are not of the responsible breed? Worry not! Purchase the Golden Lizard Doggo today and enjoy cuteness without worrying about it starving!

ResourceSink_StatueGoldenNut_C.name: Golden Nut
ResourceSink_StatueGoldenNut_C.description: It's a Golden Nut. It's shiny and its price is totally justified. Don't overthink it, you need one! Purchase a Golden Nut today! (Warning: Ingestion is not recommended).

ResourceSink_CoffeeCup_C.name: FICSIT™ Coffee Cup
ResourceSink_CoffeeCup_C.description: Worried about your superfluous body needs interrupting your work? We're proud to provide our pioneers with the means to stay efficient! Get your Coffee Cup! (Coffee not included).
